---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | AryanForge"
  description="Privacy policy for AryanForge — how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our website and services.">

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-grotesk font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">
        Privacy <span class="gradient-gold">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-2">Last updated: June 15, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 prose-body">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We collect information you voluntarily provide: name, email address, phone number, company name, website URL, project requirements, and budget information when you fill out forms on our website, interact with our AI chatbot, purchase products, or contact us.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-3">
          We automatically collect: IP address, browser type, device information, pages visited, time spent, referral source, and interaction data through cookies and similar technologies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We use your information to: (a) provide and improve our Services; (b) respond to inquiries and support requests; (c) process payments and deliver digital products; (d) send service-related communications and follow-ups; (e) qualify leads and personalize your experience; (f) analyze usage patterns to improve our website; (g) comply with legal obligations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Your data is stored securely on our infrastructure. We implement industry-standard security measures including: encryption in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest (AES-256), HMAC-signed webhooks, rate limiting, SQL injection protection, and regular security audits. Chat conversations and lead data are stored in a PostgreSQL database with access restricted to authorized personnel only.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">4. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We use essential cookies for website functionality (session management, theme preference, currency preference). We also use analytics cookies to understand usage patterns and improve our services. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings. Essential cookies cannot be disabled as they are necessary for the website to function.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-3">
          Cookies we use: <strong>Session cookies</strong> (temporary, deleted when you close your browser), <strong>Preference cookies</strong> (remember your theme and currency choices), <strong>Analytics cookies</strong> (anonymous usage data). We do not use advertising or tracking cookies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We use the following third-party services that may process your data:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed space-y-1 mt-2 list-disc list-inside">
          <li><strong>Razorpay</strong> — payment processing (your card details never reach our servers)</li>
          <li><strong>Groq / OpenAI</strong> — AI chat functionality (conversation data processed transiently)</li>
          <li><strong>Calendly</strong> — meeting scheduling</li>
          <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — optional database hosting</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-3">
          Each service has its own privacy policy governing data handling. We ensure data sharing is minimal and only for service delivery.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We retain your personal data for as long as necessary to provide our Services and comply with legal obligations. Chat conversations and lead data are retained for 12 months after your last interaction, after which they are anonymized or deleted. Payment records are retained for 7 years as required by Indian tax law.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          You have the right to: (a) access your personal data we hold; (b) request correction of inaccurate data; (c) request deletion of your data (subject to legal retention requirements); (d) withdraw consent for processing; (e) export your data in a portable format. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:aryan@launchwitharyan.ai" class="text-gold hover:text-gold-dim">aryan@launchwitharyan.ai</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">8. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information. We do not share your data with third parties for their marketing purposes. Data is only shared with the third-party services listed above as necessary to deliver our Services, or when required by law.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Our Services are not directed at individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors. If we become aware that a minor has provided us with personal data, we will delete it promptly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">10. International Data Transfers</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Your data may be processed in India and other countries where our service providers operate. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place for international data transfers in compliance with applicable data protection laws.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Significant changes will be notified via email if we have your contact information.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">12. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          For privacy-related inquiries, data requests, or concerns:
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-2">
          Email: <a href="mailto:aryan@launchwitharyan.ai" class="text-gold hover:text-gold-dim">aryan@launchwitharyan.ai</a><br />
          Response time: Within 48 hours
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .prose-body h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  .prose-body p { line-height: 1.75; }
  .prose-body ul { padding-left: 1rem; }
</style>
